@node intro "Scope or not to scope?"

	-What is SPi-Scope?

	To make it short: It is Yet Another Scope for KP`s HiPPoPlayer.

	-What does it require to work?

	An Amiga with KS 1.3, few bytes of memory, and HiP 2.12+.
	KS 2.04 and HiP 2.20+ are @{b}heavily recommended!@{ub}

	-Does it have anything special?

	Yes, it is written with pure assember. Also it (tries to =)
	draw scopes similar seen in stereosets.

	-Do I have pay anything for it?

	Nope, SPi-Scope is @{" FREEWARE " link free}. Of course if someone
	wants to send me postcard or something, then go ahead.

	-Will it take a LOT of CPU power?

	Nope, SPi-Scope runs at priority -30.

	-Does it work from WB?

	Of course, but you can't give any tooltypes.

	-Can I change that stupid default window position?

	Yes, you can. Look at @{" usage page " link usage} for more info.

	-Cool! I have to test this thingy.

	Please, go ahead.

@endnode

